(385, 1, '2021 CANNONDALE SCALPEL CARBON SE 2 MOUNTAIN BIKE', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane active&quot; id=&quot;tab-description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;CANNONDALE SCALPEL CARBON SE 2 MOUNTAIN BIKE 2021&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fast,\r\n precise, stable, the Cannondale Scalpel Carbon SE 2 Mountain Bike will \r\nexcel, be that on fast technical singletrack or in marathon races. The \r\nincredibly light frame has been engineered with innovative FlexPivot \r\nsuspension for the best possible traction and control, and both this and\r\n the RockShox fork, offer 120mm of plush travel so you\'ll roll faster \r\nand smoother over the harshest and rockiest of terrain. Using \r\nProportional Response in the design, each frame size is fine-tuned to \r\ncater for every rider in the same way, so whether you\'re on the biggest \r\nor the smallest size, you\'ll reap the same benefits.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;SPECIFICATION&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Frame&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cannondale\r\n all-new, 120mm travel, BallisTec carbon, Proportional Response Tuned, \r\nFlexPivot chainstay, PF30-83, tapered headtube, Speed Release 12mm \r\nthru-axle, Ai Offset, Stash compatible&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Rear Shock&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;RockShox SIDLuxe Select+, 2-position mode adjust, adjustable rebound&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Fork&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;RockShox SID Select, 120mm, Debonair, 15x110mm thru-axle, tapered steerer, 44mm offset&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Headset&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Integrated Sealed Bearing, tapered&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Bottom Bracket&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;SRAM DUB PF30 MTB83&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Stem&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cannondale 3, 6061 Alloy, 31.8, 7°&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Handlebar&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cannondale riser, butted 6061 Alloy, 31.8mm, 5° rise,