(246, 1, '2021 TREK Checkpoint SL F/S ROAD Frameset', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(49, 49, 49); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Checkpoint SL Frameset is a carbon gravel bike frame for epic all-road adventures. OCLV Carbon, a gravel-smoothing IsoSpeed decoupler, extra mounts for essential accessories, and massive tire clearance make it the ideal starting point for a lightweight, high-performance gravel bike build.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Checkpoint SL F/S Frameset', 'buy Checkpoint SL F/S Frameset from Toracycles 100% original', 'Checkpoint SL F/S Frameset'),
