(135, 1, '2021 TREK Slash 9.7 Mountain Bike', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(49, 49, 49); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Slash 9.7 pairs fast-rolling 29er mountain bike wheels with long travel suspension to make one speed-hungry rig that\'s perfectly suited to both rowdy trail rides and enduro races. A full carbon frame, killer suspension package, and a solid parts spec means you\'re getting awesome performance at a ridiculous value, too.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '2021 TREK Slash 9.7 Mountain Bike', 'buy 2021 TREK Slash 9.7 Mountain Bike from Toracycles 100% original', '2021 TREK Slash 9.7 Mountain Bike'),
