(315, 1, '2021 ROVAL Traverse SL WHEELS', '&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-family: Calibre, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Designed to handle everything from backcountry rock gardens to heavy days at the bike park, the Traverse SL is the definitive all-mountain wheel. A super-light, super-tough carbon fiber rim is combined with refined and ultra-dependable hub and spoke technology for a wheel that can conquer any mountain.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;', '', 'Traverse SL', 'buy Traverse SL from Toracycles 100% original', 'Traverse SL'),
(316, 1, '2021 ROVAL Traverse SL 38 WHEELS', '&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-family: Calibre, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;All the trick carbon goodness, bomber durability and big-mountain capability of the Traverse SL, but tailored for the plus-size aficionado. With a 38-mm internal rim width, the Traverse SL 38 answers the call for big mountain riders who want to run big meaty tires.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;', '', 'Traverse SL 38', 'buy Traverse SL 38 from Toracycles 100% original', 'Traverse SL 38'),
(321, 1, '2021 ROVAL Alpinist CLX WHEELS', '&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-family: Calibre, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;A pure climber\'s dream, the new Alpinist CLX is the lightest road clincher wheelset we have ever made. When climbing, mass is the enemy of performance, so we pared the Alpinist CLX down to the absolute minimum to capitalize on every precious watt of energy without sacrificing any of the strength, ride quality and durability that are crucial to long term performance and satisfaction.&lt;/span&gt;', '', 'Alpinist CLX', 'buy Alpinist CLX from Toracycles 100% original', 'Alpinist CLX'),
(317, 1, '2021 ROVAL Traverse Carbon WHEELS', '&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-family: Calibre, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;A no-holds-barred all-mountain off-road wheel, the Traverse Carbon upholds the superlative performance reputation of its more expensive brethren at a sliver of the cost. Cutting edge carbon technology combines performance with durability at a very affordable price. Everybody wins!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;', '', 'Traverse Carbon', 'buy Traverse Carbon from Toracycles 100% original', 'Traverse Carbon'),
(312, 1, '2021 ROVAL Control SL WHEELS', '&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-family: Calibre, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1240 grams is an obscenely light weight when talking about mountain bike wheelsets, the kind of weight that XC racers dream about. But light weight alone is no longer enough. So, we engineered the new Control SL wheels to be sharp handling, smooth riding, extra durable, and 22% less likely to pinch-flat your tires, in addition to being some of the lightest weight production wheels on the planet.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;', '', 'Control SL', 'buy Control SL from Toracycles 100% original', 'Control SL'),
(314, 1, '2021 ROVAL Control 29 148 WHEELS', '&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-family: Calibre, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;When you think of lightweight XC wheels, aluminum probably doesn\'t come to mind. In reality, though, high-grade alloy wheels have all of the tremendous performance properties found in carbon, like light overall weight, durability, and resilience to impact. And when made with the right hands, they\'re perfect for competitive racers and everyday trail riders alike. The problem is that, while many carbon wheels can check these boxes with ease, most alloy wheels don\'t live up to these expectations. In the case of the Control 29 wheels, however, there’s finally an aluminum wheelset that\'s truly ready to race.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;', '', 'Control 29 148', 'buy Control 29 148 from Toracycles 100% original', 'Control 29 148');
