b(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: ProximaNova-Light, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Thanks to the need to make the rim sidewalls strong enough to handle the pressure of clincher tires, these carbon rims are super-strong. Stronger than aluminum rims, so worry not about their durability. They are race light, but training wheel tough.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 20px; margin-block-start: 1em; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: ProximaNova-Light, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Sapim CX-Ray J-Bend spokes are used both front and rear to lace the rim to the hub. These spokes are light, aero, and stiff. 24 spokes, two-cross, both front and rear.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 20px; margin-block-start: 1em; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: ProximaNova-Light, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;These NSW wheels utilize Zipp’s Cognition hubs. The front features scalloped flanges for the spoke beds. J-bend spokes resist the twisting forces disc-braking can put on spokes. This results in&amp;nbsp; less pressure on the spokes, increasing lateral stiffness and durability. The rear has a pawl design with an Axial Clutch, which reduces pawl drag by 50% when coasting, and with a 36-tooth engagement, you’re driving the wheel the moment you start pedaling.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 20px; margin-block-start: 1em; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: ProximaNova-Light, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The disc-mounting method is Centerlock only. Lock ring not included. The hubs come with Zipp’s Tangente quick release skewers as well as&amp;nbsp; hand-removable end caps to fit 100x12mm and 100x15mm thru-axles in front and 142x12mm rear thru-axles.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 20px; margin-block-start: 1em; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: ProximaNova-Light, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The wheels weigh in at 1860g per set, 910g in front, 950g in back.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 20px; margin-block-start: 1em; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: ProximaNova-Light, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The wheels, sold separately as front and rear, also come with a wheel bag, a Zipp tubeless valve factory-installed, valve core removal tool, Zipp Cognition Oil, and a freehub body spacer to take the 11-speed hub down to 10-speed if you need. The single wheel bags can be secured together if you have a pair. SRAM/Shimano and Campagnolo 11-speed cassette bodies are standard; a SRAM XD-R driver can be swapped in as well.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 20px; margin-block-start: 1em; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: ProximaNova-Light, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In case you’re wondering, yes, you can use standard clincher tires and tubes. You’ll just need to remove the tubeless valve.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 20px; margin-block-start: 1em; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: 1.9em; font-family: ProximaNova-Light, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The Zipp 808 NSW Disc Tubeless Clincher is the wheel that meshes perfectly with the latest generation of disc brake triathlon and time trial bikes.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'ZIPP 808 NSW DISC TUBELESS CLINCHER FRONT WHEEL', 'buy ZIPP 808 NSW DISC TUBELESS CLINCHER FRONT WHEEL from Toracycles 100% Original', 'ZIPP 808 NSW DISC TUBELESS CLINCHER FRONT WHEEL');
