(121, 1, '2021 TREK Roscoe 20 Mountain Bike', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(49, 49, 49); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Roscoe 20 is a mid-fat kids\' mountain bike designed to build confidence on the trail. It takes cues from the adult Roscoe, but this ride was built from the ground up for kids. 2.8˝ mid-fat tires, a 1x drivetrain, and a wide-range cassette make Roscoe the ideal bike for little rippers who want to build skills and have a ridiculous amount of fun keeping up with Mom, Dad, or an older sibling. Fit for riders 45-52˝tall.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '2021 TREK Roscoe 20 Mountain Bike', 'buy 2021 TREK Roscoe 20 Mountain Bike from Toracycles 100% original', '2021 TREK Roscoe 20 Mountain Bike'),
